text: Kriti Sanon (; Hindi: कृति सैनॉन, IAST: Kriti Sainon; Punjabi: ਕ੍ਰਿਤੀ ਸਨੇਨ; born 27 July 1990) is an Indian actress. Her best known roles were in Dilwale (2015), Bareilly Ki Barfi (2017), Luka Chuppi (2019), and Housefull 4 (2019). She also has her own line of clothing. ==References== Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Indian movie actors Category:Indian television actors Category:Indian businesspeople Category:Actors from New Delhi
